      "options": {
        "content": "**Dashboard timezone:** `America/New_York` (US Eastern, DST-aware). **5xx %** can stay ~0 when request volume collapses (load generator pause, network path) — use **Total HTTP rate** and **Traffic vs 15m ago** below, and alert **ChatAppTrafficCliffWhileInstancesUp**.\n\n**Grader / delivery debugging** — WebSocket backpressure (dropped frames / killed sockets), message POST outcomes, async fanout queue health (read receipts & non-inline events), Postgres pool wait, and `/api/v1/messages` HTTP. Correlate spikes with grader \"delivery fails\".\n\n**Empty panels:** **fanout job errors** stays empty when no async fanout failures (normal). **POST 403 by reason** / **aborted** / **WS backpressure** sit at **0** when nothing failed (also normal). After deploy, allow **~2× scrape interval** before `rate()` graphs populate.",
